<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e293b; background: #f1f5f9; padding: 40px; }
        .module { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 6px solid #2563eb; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        h1 { color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        h2 { color: #2563eb; font-size: 1.4em; margin-top: 0; }
        .bilingual { color: #64748b; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.95em; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .vocab-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; background: #f8fafc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .term { font-weight: bold; color: #334155; }
        .btn-ingest { display: inline-block; margin-top: 15px; padding: 8px 16px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Formation: Vocabulaire Technique Bilingue</h1>
        <p>Cobel Business Training Center | Project ID: e3c05f2a</p>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 1: Fondamentaux Industriels</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Industrial Fundamentals</div>
        <div class="vocab-grid">
            <div><span class="term">Atelier</span> (Workshop)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Équipement</span> (Equipment)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Chaîne de montage</span> (Assembly Line)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Maintenance</span> (Maintenance)</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 2: Sécurité et Protocoles</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Safety and Protocols</div>
        <div class="vocab-grid">
            <div><span class="term">EPI</span> (PPE)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Risque d'incendie</span> (Fire Hazard)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Sortie de secours</span> (Emergency Exit)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Premiers secours</span> (First Aid)</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 3: Outils et Outillage</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Tools and Tooling</div>
        <div class="vocab-grid">
            <div><span class="term">Clé à molette</span> (Adjustable Wrench)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Perceuse</span> (Drill)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Tournevis</span> (Screwdriver)</div>
            <div><span class="term">Mesure</span> (Measurement)</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 4: Mesures et Précision</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Measurement and Precision</div>
        <p>Focus sur le calibrage et les unités de mesure techniques.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 5: Lecture de Plans</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Blueprint Reading</div>
        <p>Analyse des schémas techniques et symboles industriels.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 6: Communication d'Équipe</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Team Communication</div>
        <p>Terminologie pour les rapports de shift et la collaboration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 7: Logistique et Stockage</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Logistics and Storage</div>
        <p>Gestion d'inventaire et flux de matériaux.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="module">
        <h2>Module 8: Évaluation Finale</h2>
        <div class="bilingual">Final Assessment</div>
        <p>Utilisez l'outil "Analog-to-Digital Bridge" à droite pour soumettre votre examen manuscrit.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>